# Frontend UI standards

- **Buttons**: ensure clickable buttons use `cursor-pointer` (prefer using the shared `components/ui/Button.jsx`).
- **Surfaces**: prefer cream app surfaces via CSS tokens (`--bg`, `--surface`) and use `bg-[rgb(var(--surface))]` instead of hard-coded `bg-white` for cards/inputs/shell.

